{"tid":1396055,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］飲食業界致香港市民的公開信（附聯署）","createTime":"2019-08-02T03:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T08:07:35.000Z","uid":94128,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71ba299206189deaef382c74c9c4774e7a76af1b","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"(Please refer to #2 for the English version.)<br />\n<br />\n致各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是來自飲食業界的香港市民，包括任職各級各類的廚師、侍應等飲食業從業員，以及就讀相關課程的大專學生。有感近月香港正值多事之秋，社會撕裂嚴峻，希望透過此公開信表達我們對事件的支持和關注，並對香港政府予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n自6月9日起，香港市民針對逃犯條例（修訂）議案發起了多次大型示威行動，二百萬人以和平、理性、優雅的方式表達訴求，超過四名同伴以性命相諫；結果換來政府置若罔聞，甚至縱容警察濫權，多番使用過份武力對待示威者，眼見旺角、沙田、元朗等事件中，因警方挑釁和進逼，導致商場、食肆及民居都成為戰線，發生令人心痛的流血衝突。事件發展至今再演變為警黑合作，警察目無綱紀，肆意危害市民安全。眼見官員、警察和黑社會互相勾結，港府綱紀廢弛，以致香港「自由民主、人權法治、公平公義、誠信透明」的核心價值備受衝擊，令市民深感失望、痛心、憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥作為行政長官難辭其咎，卻毫無悔意，只和各司局長互相推卸責任，還妄語指未能找出社會問題癥結，實在有欠公允。我們深信「政治問題，政治解決」，但若然政府無心處理紛爭，繼續包庇警黑，每每在衝突過後透過記者會「譴責」示威者然後不了了之，市民亦只能在日常生活「譴責」為虎作倀的官員及警察，包括但不止於罷工、拒絕接待及服務某類人士、杯葛應徵及光顧建制派食肆或集團等等。遍地開花，指日可待。<br />\n<br />\n我們要求政府不要再玩文字遊戲，立即回應民間五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1.撤回逃犯條例修訂，<br />\n2.撤回612暴動定性，<br />\n3.撤銷示威者控罪，<br />\n4.成立獨立調查委員會，<br />\n5.落實執行雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n香 港 人 加 油<br />\n<br />\n一群飲食業人士 敬上<br />\n2019年7月28日<br />\n<br />\n連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=02c8f8cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6</a>"},{"pid":"5e0b71b03ddc1dcd9bcbe35314ba2bcb98a28d6a","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"To the people of Hong Kong,<br />\n<br />\nWe are the food and beverage industry practitioners and undergraduates. In the light of the intensified social cleavage and recent incidents which ruin the core values of Hong Kong immensely, we are writing to support the mass demonstrations against the extradition bill and to voice strong&nbsp;condemnation of the government&rsquo;s indifference, the abuse of police power and their neglect of duties.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nThere have been millions&nbsp;of anti-extradition protesters participated in peaceful, sanctioned marches&nbsp;since 9 June. At least 4 Hongkongers urged the government to fully withdraw the extradition bill by means of committing suicide. However, the government&nbsp;is still indifferent,&nbsp;turning a deaf ear&nbsp;to the people. The police violence against demonstrators and the blind eye they turned toward triad attacks on demonstrators and unarmed civilians are intolerable. We are aggrieved that autonomy and freedoms promised under One Country Two Systems have been severely eroded and deprived.<br />\n<br />\nChief Executive&nbsp;Carrie Lam and her authoritarian government&rsquo;s attempt to pass the extradition bill&nbsp;and their indifference towards appeals of the people are obviously the root causes of the recent social unrest. There is no doubt that the rule of law and social order in Hong Kong can only be restored by the government responding to people&rsquo;s 5 demands as follows,<br />\n<br />\n1. Complete withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the characterisations of the protest on 12 June 2019 as &ldquo;riots&rdquo;<br />\n3. Establishment of an independent investigation committee chaired by retired judges to investigate the police&rsquo;s actions<br />\n4. The Department of Justice maintains its political neutrality and not conduct political prosecutions<br />\n5. Implementation of Dual Universal Suffrage in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nIf the government keeps playing with language and fails to truly respond to the demands above, people will have no choice but to chastise the government officials and police officers involved in legitimate means, including but not limited to strike, refuse service, boycott the recruitment of F&amp;B groups and restaurants owned by members&nbsp;of the&nbsp;pro-establishment&nbsp;camp.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nFight for freedom! Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom a group of Food &amp; Beverage practitioners and students<br />\n28 July 2019<br />\n<br />\nLink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjIv2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=02c8f8cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/7FQpCcsS9ThkPseV6</a>"},{"pid":"000d5f637cf50946f1fdc1f7852976d5c2e6c76c","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cFO9Cj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cFO9Cj.jpg&h=0403572b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dmR7o0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dmR7o0.jpg&h=ae96a383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLmVPCn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLmVPCn.jpg&h=c4149ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqE8qaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqE8qaK.jpg&h=13090cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ljik0J5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjik0J5.jpg&h=22327f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFDhivN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFDhivN.jpg&h=89dae617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88zwnXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88zwnXt.jpg&h=a791b63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A02YNo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA02YNo9.jpg&h=ecbb357a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38FGLaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38FGLaR.jpg&h=27c373fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"323079267b83b136bb9c608457da300f25d95c54","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日齊罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d38fbe514053829efa12e39a40bebf6d136c502","tid":1396055,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"快D搵個人出黎踢走20蚊張啦"},{"pid":"893197e4fe0603342ab9ea6a3bc39f536bc4b9b6","tid":1396055,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廚房佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83282479466e70979cb9891c100b83838c97835","tid":1396055,"uid":191527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"凍撚茶"},{"pid":"976016996e81e6601a0af4f26660e3db67cdf5e3","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d38fbe514053829efa12e39a40bebf6d136c502","tid":1396055,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"快D搵個人出黎踢走20蚊張啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"有諗過咁做！但成立工會需要好多程序，俾啲時間，我相信有人會企出黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7f8e2f8d9b9e806a361193fddcb241bb1b5b80","tid":1396055,"uid":268241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009b52961fe493e28a7de93d9e5ca48e23d1075e","tid":1396055,"uid":94128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"普遍認知飲食業都多深藍，但我地想大家知道其實仲有唔少黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 業界朋友you are not alone"},{"pid":"c943ee0e04adb3148d3fba75f2f50f002b948554","tid":1396055,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力